      <p class="font-sora text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">A documented, hand-raised Congo cannot honestly be produced for $850. When you see that figure, you are looking at a bird missing everything above — or a listing with no real bird behind it at all. The gap is not markup. It is paperwork, health, and accountability.</p>

